        <Parent_String>cellulose (complex carbohydrate) [300012861], cellulose and cellulose by product [300248124], organic material [300011792], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
